WEBVTT

01:11.800 --> 01:12.440
Xu Xiao.

01:14.480 --> 01:15.010
Xiaocen.

01:16.320 --> 01:17.920
Aren't you going back today?

01:18.280 --> 01:19.210
I'm not leaving.

01:24.200 --> 01:24.930
Not leaving?

01:26.880 --> 01:27.840
You told me

01:28.440 --> 01:29.720
to follow my heart.

01:32.440 --> 01:34.300
I thought about it for a long time.

01:34.560 --> 01:35.960
I used to be too cowardly.

01:36.920 --> 01:39.780
I was afraid to bear the consequences of my choices.

01:40.039 --> 01:40.800
So before,

01:40.800 --> 01:43.000
my family always made decisions for me.

01:46.360 --> 01:47.000
But now,

01:47.000 --> 01:49.330
I have the courage to choose my own future,

01:49.560 --> 01:51.890
and the courage to bear the consequences.

01:55.600 --> 01:56.660
So I'm going to stay

01:57.280 --> 01:58.600
and do what I like to do.

02:00.000 --> 02:00.840
With you.

02:17.200 --> 02:17.800
So

02:19.000 --> 02:20.800
you're not changing your major?

02:22.040 --> 02:23.040
And this holiday,

02:23.040 --> 02:24.440
I'll stay in Jingdezhen.

02:30.320 --> 02:31.120
What's wrong?

02:31.640 --> 02:32.600
This holiday,

02:34.280 --> 02:35.680
I won't be in Jingdezhen.

02:37.280 --> 02:37.920
Why?

02:41.320 --> 02:42.040
Well,

02:42.680 --> 02:43.740
it's the holidays.

02:43.960 --> 02:45.800
I saw there were fewer people on the court,

02:45.800 --> 02:47.730
so I decided to stretch my muscles.

02:49.079 --> 02:51.360
And I ran into an old classmate of mine.

02:51.560 --> 02:53.020
He refused to admit defeat

02:53.360 --> 02:55.560
and insisted on playing one-on-one with me.

02:55.560 --> 02:56.400
So we played.

02:56.400 --> 02:57.520
For over a dozen rounds,

02:57.520 --> 02:59.320
he couldn't defend a single one.

02:59.520 --> 03:00.800
As a result, extreme joy turned to sorrow,

03:00.800 --> 03:02.330
and I got injured in combat.

03:03.880 --> 03:04.740
Never mind him.

03:05.720 --> 03:06.920
Fortunately, my wife

03:07.200 --> 03:08.000
isn't at home.

03:09.040 --> 03:10.500
Let me tell you something.

03:10.680 --> 03:11.120
Go ahead.

03:11.120 --> 03:12.920
So, an old friend of mine

03:13.800 --> 03:15.060
asked me a long time ago

03:15.280 --> 03:17.480
to restore a batch of porcelain for him.

03:18.040 --> 03:19.079
I promised him.

03:19.960 --> 03:21.890
I think you can complete this task.

03:22.280 --> 03:24.160
It's just that the place is a bit far.

03:24.160 --> 03:24.680
Where?

03:25.720 --> 03:26.400
Malaysia.

03:29.040 --> 03:30.240
I wanted to give you some time

03:30.240 --> 03:31.240
to think it over.

03:32.160 --> 03:34.160
So I accepted Mr. Yue's commission.

03:35.400 --> 03:36.930
I didn't expect you to stay.

03:41.040 --> 03:41.800
It's okay.

03:44.280 --> 03:45.280
I'll wait for you.

04:20.160 --> 04:20.560
Hello.

04:20.880 --> 04:21.279
Hello.

04:21.440 --> 04:22.500
You must be Xu Xiao.

04:22.840 --> 04:24.120
I'm Mr. Zeng's grandson.

04:24.120 --> 04:24.920
My name is Zeng Yi.

04:24.920 --> 04:26.180
You can call me Justin.

04:26.200 --> 04:27.400
Welcome to Malaysia.

04:27.680 --> 04:28.840
Let me help you with your luggage.

04:28.840 --> 04:29.440
No thanks.

04:29.640 --> 04:30.370
I can manage.

04:30.400 --> 04:30.730
Okay.

04:34.480 --> 04:34.840
This way.

04:34.840 --> 04:35.200
Okay.

04:41.040 --> 04:42.570
Grandpa, the guest is here.

04:43.640 --> 04:44.240
After you.

04:47.440 --> 04:48.000
Mr. Zeng.

04:48.680 --> 04:49.280
Hello.

04:49.680 --> 04:51.200
You must be Mr. Yue's student.

04:51.200 --> 04:52.240
I am Zeng Yuren.

04:52.560 --> 04:53.680
Nice to meet you.

04:54.200 --> 04:54.860
I am Xu Xiao.

04:55.159 --> 04:56.090
Nice to meet you.

05:02.560 --> 05:04.560
Xiaocen, I've arrived in Malaysia.

05:05.640 --> 05:06.640
You must be tired.

05:07.120 --> 05:07.980
How do you feel?

05:08.600 --> 05:09.880
Not bad. Pretty good.

05:12.200 --> 05:13.400
Where are you now?

05:14.560 --> 05:15.600
I'm at Mr. Zeng's house.

05:15.600 --> 05:18.360
What kind of person is Mr. Zeng?

05:19.480 --> 05:22.560
He seems to be a Malaysian-Chinese entrepreneur.

05:25.000 --> 05:26.680
Then what kind of

05:26.680 --> 05:28.320
porcelain does he want you to restore?

05:28.320 --> 05:29.250
I'm not sure yet.

05:29.960 --> 05:32.120
He doesn't seem to trust me much.

05:34.200 --> 05:35.600
I believe you can do it.

05:39.000 --> 05:39.640
Well,

05:40.200 --> 05:41.440
it's quite late now.

05:42.560 --> 05:43.690
Get some early rest.

05:43.800 --> 05:45.000
Let's talk tomorrow.

05:46.080 --> 05:46.520
Okay.

05:47.880 --> 05:48.280
Bye.

05:49.480 --> 05:49.960
Bye.

05:57.840 --> 05:58.720
Malaysia.

06:00.800 --> 06:02.440
Mr. Yue recommended him to go to Malaysia

06:02.440 --> 06:03.640
to help an overseas Chinese entrepreneur

06:03.640 --> 06:04.960
complete the restoration work.

06:04.960 --> 06:06.760
So you stayed in Jingdezhen

06:07.120 --> 06:08.180
and he went abroad.

06:09.360 --> 06:10.490
When will he be back?

06:11.720 --> 06:14.180
He'll probably be there the whole vacation.

06:15.440 --> 06:16.160
Yuexin.

06:16.600 --> 06:17.720
I really envy you.

06:18.280 --> 06:20.000
You get to do your vacation part-time job

06:20.000 --> 06:21.640
and work with Qi Yi.

06:25.240 --> 06:25.770
Xiaocen.

06:26.600 --> 06:27.320
I think

06:27.840 --> 06:29.200
Xu Xiao didn't just go to Malaysia

06:29.200 --> 06:30.800
to restore cultural relics.

06:31.000 --> 06:31.600
Look.

06:33.280 --> 06:34.740
I saw this project before.

06:35.400 --> 06:36.840
This overseas Chinese is a board member

06:36.840 --> 06:38.640
of a top university in Malaysia.

06:38.640 --> 06:39.840
Their school and ours

06:39.840 --> 06:41.600
have a year-round exchange student program.

06:41.600 --> 06:42.659
Exchange student?

06:43.080 --> 06:44.920
They provide full scholarships

06:45.440 --> 06:46.040
and also

06:46.040 --> 06:48.280
opportunities to participate in national cultural relic restoration.

06:48.280 --> 06:49.840
A lot of people are competing for this.

06:49.840 --> 06:52.440
Mr. Yue just wants to send Xu Xiao

06:52.600 --> 06:54.240
there as an exchange student.

06:54.240 --> 06:55.640
Is this an interview too?

06:56.280 --> 06:56.960
Probably.

07:04.600 --> 07:05.530
Sorry, Xiaocen.

07:06.080 --> 07:07.340
I've been busy all day,

07:07.440 --> 07:08.960
so I'm just calling you back now.

07:08.960 --> 07:09.640
It's fine.

07:11.640 --> 07:12.720
How was your day?

07:13.800 --> 07:14.480
I'm currently staying at

07:14.480 --> 07:16.240
Mr. Yue's overseas Chinese friend's place.

07:16.240 --> 07:19.100
At Mr. Zeng's, the one who accepted the commission.

07:19.240 --> 07:21.640
They are restoring a batch of Ming Dynasty porcelain this time.

07:21.640 --> 07:22.720
They are all very precious.

07:22.720 --> 07:24.450
It's hard to see them back home.

07:25.000 --> 07:25.800
Really?

07:27.200 --> 07:28.680
Because they were salvaged from the seabed,

07:28.680 --> 07:30.140
they are highly corroded.

07:30.320 --> 07:31.560
I need to desalinate them

07:31.560 --> 07:33.020
and restore their colors.

07:34.840 --> 07:36.360
Can you fix them?

07:37.080 --> 07:37.920
Of course.

07:38.440 --> 07:40.360
Even though it's just me doing this,

07:40.360 --> 07:41.480
and the workload is a bit heavy,

07:41.480 --> 07:43.210
a college student will help me.

07:44.000 --> 07:45.460
A student from over there?

07:45.600 --> 07:46.000
Yes.

07:46.640 --> 07:49.360
Someone studying restoration at a local university.

07:49.360 --> 07:50.360
He is also a student of

07:50.360 --> 07:53.490
the Cultural Relics Conservation major at this school.

07:53.800 --> 07:56.440
How is the university there?

07:56.640 --> 07:57.760
It's very good.

07:57.920 --> 08:00.050
It's the best university in Malaysia.

08:00.840 --> 08:03.160
Their Cultural Relics Conservation major is also very good.

08:03.160 --> 08:05.360
The restoration courses are very professional,

08:05.360 --> 08:07.520
and their equipment is even better than our school's.

08:07.520 --> 08:08.440
So,

08:10.120 --> 08:11.850
you also like that school a lot.

08:13.040 --> 08:13.840
I like it a lot.

08:14.080 --> 08:14.680
Oh, right.

08:15.080 --> 08:16.320
After this batch of porcelain is restored,

08:16.320 --> 08:18.600
they will be exhibited in the school's Chinese Museum.

08:18.600 --> 08:19.280
When the time comes,

08:19.280 --> 08:21.000
Mr. Zeng will take us to see

08:21.400 --> 08:23.000
the results of our hard work.

08:24.360 --> 08:25.080
Is that so?

08:26.360 --> 08:28.160
Mr. Zeng is a director of this school.

08:28.160 --> 08:29.490
He's highly respected.

08:30.200 --> 08:30.880
Do you

08:33.120 --> 08:34.840
have anything else to tell me?

08:35.440 --> 08:36.240
Nothing else.

08:36.880 --> 08:38.809
It's basically the same every day.

08:43.600 --> 08:44.400
What's wrong?

08:45.440 --> 08:46.320
I'm fine.

08:47.640 --> 08:48.280
I'm fine.

08:50.600 --> 08:51.800
Are you going to rest?

08:52.200 --> 08:53.280
It's getting late.

08:54.200 --> 08:55.840
I still need to gather some

08:55.840 --> 08:56.960
materials for tomorrow's restoration.

08:56.960 --> 08:58.360
I'll need them tomorrow.

08:59.040 --> 09:00.040
I'll go rest then.

09:00.400 --> 09:01.400
I'll hang up then.

09:14.960 --> 09:15.640
Xiaocen,

09:16.480 --> 09:18.160
hasn't Xu Xiao told you

09:18.480 --> 09:21.080
that he might go abroad as an exchange student?

09:23.840 --> 09:27.040
He might be busy recently,

09:28.040 --> 09:29.680
working on the restoration.

09:30.240 --> 09:31.080
I think

09:31.440 --> 09:33.500
he's having too much fun in Malaysia.

09:33.680 --> 09:35.240
You two will be apart for two years, and he doesn't even care.

09:35.240 --> 09:36.080
Yan Xue,

09:36.240 --> 09:38.440
Xu Xiao hasn't decided to go abroad yet.

09:39.320 --> 09:41.360
Maybe Xu Xiao has his own plans.

09:41.680 --> 09:44.200
He might want to discuss it with Xiaocen after coming back.

09:44.200 --> 09:45.880
If he's decided not to study abroad,

09:45.880 --> 09:47.340
why doesn't he just say it?

09:47.360 --> 09:50.080
There's definitely a problem with him hiding it like this.

09:50.080 --> 09:52.320
If Xu Xiao has such a good opportunity,

09:54.320 --> 09:55.720
I think he should take it.

09:57.600 --> 09:58.520
Xiaocen,

09:58.600 --> 10:00.260
don't always think of others.

10:00.480 --> 10:02.160
If you really want him to stay,

10:02.280 --> 10:04.000
just tell him directly.

10:07.200 --> 10:09.680
I think it's Xu Xiao's own decision.

10:10.880 --> 10:12.810
I don't want to interfere with him.

10:13.960 --> 10:15.490
Let him choose for himself.

10:17.320 --> 10:18.640
I can't stand it anymore. I'll talk to him.

10:18.640 --> 10:19.320
Yan Xue.

10:19.800 --> 10:22.000
This is Xiaocen and Xu Xiao's own business.

10:22.000 --> 10:23.000
Don't interfere.

10:24.640 --> 10:25.200
Fine.

10:27.480 --> 10:28.200
Xiaocen,

10:28.840 --> 10:31.520
if Xu Xiao really decides

10:31.640 --> 10:32.800
to study abroad,

10:34.080 --> 10:35.940
have you thought about what to do?

10:42.160 --> 10:43.400
How's the work going?

10:45.880 --> 10:48.280
The restoration work is going pretty well.

10:48.400 --> 10:49.440
Mr. Zeng also said

10:49.440 --> 10:51.970
he would give me more restoration work later.

10:53.720 --> 10:54.780
Congratulations.

10:55.040 --> 10:56.960
The restoration environment here is great.

10:56.960 --> 10:58.760
And the schools here in Malaysia

10:59.200 --> 11:00.160
have specially set up

11:00.160 --> 11:02.040
a dedicated X-ray spectrometer.

11:03.080 --> 11:05.200
It can test the age and composition

11:05.200 --> 11:06.130
of the ceramics.

11:06.400 --> 11:08.880
I've only seen it in the provincial museum before.

11:08.880 --> 11:10.010
Do you want to see it?

11:10.240 --> 11:12.040
I'll show it to you on video later.

11:12.040 --> 11:13.240
I don't want to see it.

11:13.480 --> 11:14.880
You don't need to show me.

11:17.720 --> 11:18.520
What's wrong?

11:20.000 --> 11:20.530
Nothing.

11:22.040 --> 11:23.770
I know you're doing well there.

11:24.840 --> 11:26.370
And I know it's great there.

11:30.720 --> 11:32.360
Then continue with your restoration.

11:32.360 --> 11:33.220
I'm hanging up.

11:33.640 --> 11:35.370
But we haven't talked for long.

11:47.280 --> 11:48.480
Xiaocen, come here.

11:49.280 --> 11:51.280
Try the persimmon. It's very sweet.

11:53.880 --> 11:55.210
What's wrong, Xiaocen?

11:55.320 --> 11:57.250
Tell me if you have any grievances.

12:03.480 --> 12:04.080
Xiaocen,

12:04.720 --> 12:06.250
what are your thoughts now?

12:07.600 --> 12:09.460
If he has already made up his mind,

12:10.160 --> 12:11.220
I will support him.

12:15.600 --> 12:16.280
Xiaocen,

12:16.880 --> 12:18.560
you are a very kind girl

12:19.360 --> 12:21.290
and always considerate of others.

12:21.400 --> 12:23.600
But you should also think for yourself.

12:24.080 --> 12:26.680
You have the right to pursue your own happiness

12:26.960 --> 12:28.520
and fight for what you want.

12:32.720 --> 12:34.920
I'm afraid he'll think I'm too selfish.

12:36.440 --> 12:38.480
Maybe he has already made his decision.

12:38.480 --> 12:39.940
Overthinking is useless.

12:41.440 --> 12:43.160
If you don't say some things out loud,

12:43.160 --> 12:44.890
you will never know the answer.

12:45.480 --> 12:47.480
You must be brave to speak your mind.

12:47.840 --> 12:49.770
Don't be afraid of being rejected.

12:50.600 --> 12:52.860
At least you won't regret it if you tried.

12:54.840 --> 12:56.920
I just don't know how to say it.

13:01.160 --> 13:03.120
If you really care about him

13:03.760 --> 13:05.240
and don't want him to leave you,

13:05.240 --> 13:06.640
then you should tell him.

13:07.160 --> 13:08.200
Your relationship

13:08.200 --> 13:09.720
is worth trying for once.

13:10.440 --> 13:12.440
Don't let yourself regret it later.

13:12.520 --> 13:13.480
Aunt.

13:15.080 --> 13:16.160
When I was young,

13:16.160 --> 13:17.400
I was reckless for love

13:17.400 --> 13:19.000
and did a lot of silly things.

13:20.240 --> 13:21.480
Now it seems

13:22.520 --> 13:23.800
that my love was misplaced.

13:23.800 --> 13:24.800
But I don't regret

13:25.360 --> 13:26.240
any choice I made at that time.

13:26.240 --> 13:27.840
Young people should be brave

13:29.320 --> 13:31.400
and leave no regrets for themselves.

13:32.080 --> 13:33.280
Xiaocen,

13:40.040 --> 13:40.970
what is the thing

13:41.480 --> 13:43.480
you want to do most

13:43.720 --> 13:45.000
in your mind right now?

13:50.480 --> 13:51.880
I want to go to Malaysia.

13:53.760 --> 13:54.280
What?

13:54.760 --> 13:56.090
I want to go to Malaysia.

14:01.600 --> 14:02.320
Xiaocen,

14:02.800 --> 14:04.120
is it possible

14:04.200 --> 14:05.840
that you can just make a phone call?

14:05.840 --> 14:06.770
I want to see him.

14:07.760 --> 14:09.290
I want to tell him in person.

14:12.520 --> 14:13.640
You are an adult.

14:14.200 --> 14:14.640
Are you

14:15.280 --> 14:16.240
really sure?

14:18.120 --> 14:19.920
I don't want to be timid anymore.

14:20.400 --> 14:21.860
I want to tell him in person

14:22.480 --> 14:24.280
that I don't want him to leave me.

14:39.280 --> 14:40.540
Do you have a passport?

14:40.720 --> 14:41.080
Yes.

14:42.280 --> 14:44.000
Malaysia is visa-free.

14:44.240 --> 14:46.760
Take the high-speed rail to Shanghai,

14:47.280 --> 14:49.920
and then fly from Shanghai.

14:51.120 --> 14:51.840
Aunt,

14:52.080 --> 14:53.320
you mean I should

14:53.720 --> 14:54.120
go?

14:55.040 --> 14:56.600
I'll handle your mom.

14:57.080 --> 14:58.040
Thank you, Aunt.

15:00.800 --> 15:01.760
Aunt,

15:02.080 --> 15:03.760
you're the best.

15:05.920 --> 15:07.180
Running away for love?

15:07.320 --> 15:09.450
I have plenty of experience with that.

15:13.840 --> 15:14.440
Qingfang,

15:14.720 --> 15:15.520
is it this one?

15:15.680 --> 15:16.200
Yes.

15:16.520 --> 15:17.320
Thanks, Xing.

15:18.280 --> 15:18.760
Mom,

15:19.120 --> 15:20.840
can't I go to Malaysia with you?

15:20.840 --> 15:21.840
Of course you can't.

15:21.840 --> 15:23.040
You need to stay at home and behave.

15:23.040 --> 15:24.960
You haven't even finished your summer homework.

15:24.960 --> 15:25.560
All right.

15:25.800 --> 15:26.360
Xiaocen.

15:27.040 --> 15:28.770
I've booked the ticket for you.

15:29.480 --> 15:30.410
Thank you, Aunt.

15:31.240 --> 15:32.000
If you need anything there,

15:32.000 --> 15:33.360
call me, okay?

15:42.400 --> 15:43.000
Xiaocen.

15:43.360 --> 15:44.760
I've called a car for you.

15:45.440 --> 15:46.370
Thank you, Aunt.

15:47.280 --> 15:48.080
I believe you

15:48.240 --> 15:50.100
will definitely enjoy this trip.

15:50.520 --> 15:51.080
I will.

15:53.280 --> 15:54.320
Xing,

15:54.320 --> 15:54.850
goodbye.

15:55.280 --> 15:56.680
Alright, hurry up and go.

15:57.040 --> 15:58.300
I'm leaving now, Aunt.

15:59.880 --> 16:00.680
Go.

16:08.800 --> 16:10.660
Thank you, Aunt. You're the best.

16:11.120 --> 16:12.850
You are amazing, you know that?

16:13.880 --> 16:15.120
Alright, hurry up and go.

16:15.120 --> 16:15.960
If you go any later,

16:15.960 --> 16:17.220
you'll miss the train.

16:17.840 --> 16:18.770
I'm leaving now.

16:19.200 --> 16:20.040
Goodbye, Xing.

16:20.040 --> 16:20.570
Goodbye.

16:23.280 --> 16:23.800
Bye.

16:40.960 --> 16:42.020
Xiaocen, Xiaocen.

16:44.080 --> 16:45.940
Didn't I tell you guys not to come?

16:46.280 --> 16:47.320
Such a spectacular scene.

16:47.320 --> 16:48.450
How could I not come?

16:48.520 --> 16:49.120
Xiaocen.

16:49.240 --> 16:50.280
Have you really made up your mind

16:50.280 --> 16:51.840
to go to Malaysia alone?

16:52.000 --> 16:53.330
You didn't tell Xu Xiao?

16:53.640 --> 16:55.440
You can't tell Xu Xiao, Xiaocen.

16:55.520 --> 16:56.360
The best way

16:56.360 --> 16:58.220
is to go straight to his workplace

16:58.360 --> 16:59.890
and confront him directly.

16:59.960 --> 17:00.680
That works best.

17:00.680 --> 17:01.560
That won't work.

17:01.560 --> 17:03.200
Xiaocen is going to Malaysia alone.

17:03.200 --> 17:04.240
She's not familiar with the place.

17:04.240 --> 17:05.440
What if she gets lost?

17:06.079 --> 17:06.760
No way.

17:06.760 --> 17:07.480
She's a grown adult.

17:07.480 --> 17:08.480
How could she get lost?

17:08.480 --> 17:10.810
But I really didn't tell Xu Xiao this time.

17:11.240 --> 17:12.400
I want to surprise him.

17:12.400 --> 17:14.260
You have to keep it a secret for me.

17:14.480 --> 17:15.520
I get it.

17:15.960 --> 17:17.000
Don't worry, Xiaocen.

17:17.000 --> 17:18.440
We will keep it a secret for you.

17:18.440 --> 17:19.280
Xiaocen, let me tell you.

17:19.280 --> 17:20.210
You have no idea.

17:20.760 --> 17:21.920
Wu Jing called.

17:22.200 --> 17:23.660
She misses you like crazy.

17:24.040 --> 17:24.640
Xiaocen.

17:25.200 --> 17:26.440
You must be careful.

17:26.560 --> 17:27.480
I know.

17:27.480 --> 17:28.840
Call me if anything happens.

17:28.840 --> 17:29.800
Just rest assured.

17:29.800 --> 17:30.200
Don't worry.

17:30.200 --> 17:31.680
We all said a proper goodbye to her.

17:31.680 --> 17:32.720
That's it then. Bye.

17:32.720 --> 17:34.360
Bye, bye.

17:46.200 --> 17:46.680
Bye.

17:49.760 --> 17:50.360
That's great.

17:50.360 --> 17:51.490
You guys go back now.

18:55.520 --> 18:56.240
Hello.

18:56.800 --> 18:57.320
Hello.

18:57.320 --> 18:57.880
Hello.

18:58.040 --> 19:00.570
Excuse me, do you know how to get to this place?

19:00.640 --> 19:01.520
You go this way.

19:01.520 --> 19:02.440
Go to the front first.

19:02.440 --> 19:04.170
Then go straight and turn left,

19:04.280 --> 19:05.410
and you'll be there.

19:06.600 --> 19:07.480
Excuse me.

19:08.040 --> 19:09.440
First walk to that house,

19:09.680 --> 19:10.800
go to the front,

19:11.040 --> 19:13.900
then go straight and turn left, and you'll be there.

19:14.880 --> 19:15.810
Okay, thank you.

20:18.680 --> 20:19.610
Hello, Xiaocen.

20:20.680 --> 20:21.560
Hello, Xu Xiao.

20:22.880 --> 20:24.940
When are you coming to Malacca today?

20:25.880 --> 20:27.610
I probably can't make it today.

20:27.680 --> 20:29.120
Mr. Zeng's rheumatism is acting up again.

20:29.120 --> 20:30.520
You're not coming today?

20:31.280 --> 20:32.920
Maybe I'll go tomorrow.

20:33.760 --> 20:35.690
Then when are you coming tomorrow?

20:35.960 --> 20:39.020
That depends on how Mr. Zeng's rheumatism is tomorrow.

20:41.520 --> 20:42.050
Xiaocen.

20:42.560 --> 20:44.090
Did you call for something?

20:44.640 --> 20:45.200
Nothing.

20:45.800 --> 20:46.200
I...

20:46.440 --> 20:47.440
I was just asking.

20:49.440 --> 20:50.440
Where are you now?

20:51.760 --> 20:52.160
I'm...

20:52.720 --> 20:53.720
I'm at home.

20:54.400 --> 20:55.930
I still have some work to do.

20:56.120 --> 20:57.080
I'll call you back later

20:57.080 --> 20:58.280
when I'm done, okay?

20:59.000 --> 20:59.640
Okay.

21:00.040 --> 21:00.600
Alright.

21:15.560 --> 21:16.520
Malacca.

21:16.840 --> 21:17.520
Where is he?

21:18.400 --> 21:19.200
Kuala Lumpur.

21:21.200 --> 21:21.760
Xiaocen.

21:22.040 --> 21:24.560
I anticipated you would run into great difficulties,

21:24.560 --> 21:26.440
but I didn't expect it to be this outrageous.

21:26.440 --> 21:27.440
Xiao... Xiaocen.

21:27.600 --> 21:28.960
Don't panic. Listen to me.

21:28.960 --> 21:29.800
I checked.

21:29.920 --> 21:32.000
The distance from Malacca to Kuala Lumpur isn't far.

21:32.000 --> 21:32.960
Are you going to wait for Xu Xiao,

21:32.960 --> 21:34.360
or go find him in Malacca?

21:34.400 --> 21:34.800
I...

21:34.920 --> 21:36.560
She doesn't even know where she is.

21:36.560 --> 21:38.920
I don't know what to do right now.

21:40.880 --> 21:42.760
I'll just wait for him here.

21:42.960 --> 21:44.000
Okay, that works.

21:44.000 --> 21:44.960
Don't panic.

21:45.200 --> 21:46.080
I'll try to figure something out.

21:46.080 --> 21:46.760
Please don't worry.

21:46.760 --> 21:47.640
Keep in touch.

21:47.640 --> 21:49.440
Update me on your situation at all times.

21:49.440 --> 21:50.370
Call me anytime.

21:50.480 --> 21:50.880
Okay.

21:51.040 --> 21:52.500
Okay, please don't worry.

22:23.560 --> 22:24.760
No, I have to tell Xu Xiao.

22:24.760 --> 22:25.240
No,

22:25.400 --> 22:26.360
this should be a surprise.

22:26.360 --> 22:28.620
Don't turn a surprise into a shock, okay?

22:28.840 --> 22:30.280
Xiaocen is lost now.

22:30.400 --> 22:31.730
What if she's in danger?

22:32.440 --> 22:33.320
She's an adult.

22:33.320 --> 22:34.360
She won't be in danger.

22:34.360 --> 22:34.920
After the college entrance exam,

22:34.920 --> 22:36.720
I traveled around Europe alone and I was fine.

22:36.720 --> 22:37.600
How could she be in trouble?

22:37.600 --> 22:37.960
She won't be.

22:37.960 --> 22:38.760
You are you,

22:38.760 --> 22:39.800
and Xiaocen is Xiaocen.

22:39.800 --> 22:42.080
Xiaocen doesn't have much experience going abroad.

22:42.080 --> 22:43.120
No, I have to tell Xu Xiao.

22:43.120 --> 22:43.560
No,

22:43.760 --> 22:44.640
this should be a surprise.

22:44.640 --> 22:45.400
Give it to me.

22:45.560 --> 22:47.160
No, she will be in danger.

22:47.160 --> 22:48.290
I want to protect...

22:54.800 --> 22:55.880
Hello, Xu Xiao.

22:56.520 --> 22:57.450
Hello, Xiaocen.

22:59.120 --> 23:01.360
I'm really looking forward to going to Malacca tomorrow.

23:01.360 --> 23:02.080
Are you?

23:02.600 --> 23:05.130
Because Malacca is a very interesting place.

23:05.200 --> 23:06.000
You know what?

23:06.200 --> 23:07.880
The restaurant called Xia Xiyang

23:07.880 --> 23:08.810
is a scenic spot.

23:09.560 --> 23:10.880
To the east of that restaurant,

23:10.880 --> 23:13.540
there is a very beautiful Chinese neighborhood

23:13.560 --> 23:14.820
called Jonker Street.

23:16.280 --> 23:17.010
I really hope

23:17.600 --> 23:19.400
we can take a good walk together.

23:21.240 --> 23:24.040
There are very beautiful Nyonya buildings there.

23:24.040 --> 23:25.700
Walking through that street,

23:25.880 --> 23:27.610
you can see a beautiful bridge.

23:28.240 --> 23:29.280
On the bridge, you can see

23:29.280 --> 23:30.680
the English letters 'Welcome to the Historic City,

23:30.680 --> 23:31.960
Malacca'.

23:33.640 --> 23:36.120
From the bridge, you can see the beautiful Malacca River.

23:36.120 --> 23:39.050
On both sides of the river are beautiful riverwalks.

23:39.280 --> 23:39.880
Here,

23:40.440 --> 23:42.520
you can overlook the Strait of Malacca,

23:42.520 --> 23:44.280
and the scenery of the old town of Malacca

23:44.280 --> 23:45.160
is in full view.

23:46.080 --> 23:46.880
Further ahead

23:47.040 --> 23:48.770
is the famous Dutch Red Square.

23:49.440 --> 23:50.970
It is a landmark of Malacca.

23:51.680 --> 23:52.560
At the same time,

23:52.560 --> 23:55.620
it is also the oldest Dutch building in Southeast Asia.

23:56.120 --> 23:56.850
Legend has it

23:57.200 --> 23:59.440
that it was built by the Dutch colonial government at the time,

23:59.440 --> 24:01.000
specifically using red bricks brought over from the Netherlands,

24:01.000 --> 24:01.720
which is why

24:02.480 --> 24:04.120
it is called the Red Square.

24:05.280 --> 24:06.640
The famous Malacca red

24:07.080 --> 24:08.080
comes from this.

24:09.560 --> 24:10.360
In Red Square,

24:10.880 --> 24:13.280
there is the famous Malacca Christ Church.

24:13.520 --> 24:15.780
It's the most romantic place in Malacca.

24:16.480 --> 24:17.140
This place,

24:17.480 --> 24:19.680
there are usually a lot of artists here.

24:20.120 --> 24:20.480
Yes.

24:20.960 --> 24:22.920
Including an older man playing guitar

24:22.920 --> 24:24.040
in black clothes.

24:25.200 --> 24:26.530
He's performing today.

24:50.480 --> 24:50.960
Hello, Xu Xiao.

24:50.960 --> 24:51.820
Hello, Yuexin.

24:52.040 --> 24:53.040
I have something to tell you.

24:53.040 --> 24:54.440
Please don't get excited.

24:54.440 --> 24:55.240
It's just that

24:55.240 --> 24:57.100
Xiaocen has arrived in Malaysia.

24:57.400 --> 24:58.800
She arrived in Malaysia?

25:06.520 --> 25:07.080
Xu Xiao.

25:11.800 --> 25:12.400
I'm sorry.

25:13.280 --> 25:14.610
I wanted to come over...

25:34.120 --> 25:35.720
I've cleaned up the room upstairs.

25:35.720 --> 25:36.780
You can stay there.

25:37.600 --> 25:39.480
Sorry for the trouble.

25:40.000 --> 25:41.260
It's the least I can do.

25:41.600 --> 25:43.240
Xu Xiao helped me a lot,

25:43.560 --> 25:45.080
so I should treat you well.

25:46.400 --> 25:48.660
It hasn't been this lively in a long time.

25:48.680 --> 25:51.040
You show them around Malacca today.

25:51.640 --> 25:51.840
Okay.

25:51.840 --> 25:54.280
An old guy like me won't join you.

25:55.920 --> 25:57.050
Thank you, Mr. Zeng.

26:01.120 --> 26:02.650
Look at the buildings here.

26:03.360 --> 26:04.490
Aren't they pretty?

26:05.480 --> 26:06.140
Beautiful.

26:28.480 --> 26:30.280
Look at these porcelain shards.

26:38.240 --> 26:40.640
Look, these are all part of the collection.

26:56.600 --> 26:57.530
It's over there.

27:00.240 --> 27:01.800
Your hand is so much bigger than mine.

27:01.800 --> 27:02.560
Your hand is so small.
